[2;36m│[0m ## Summary                                                                   [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m ### detailed_summary                                                         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m Successfully discovered and exploited a **Server-Side Template Injection     [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m (SSTI)** vulnerability in the Swift Shipping & Transport Inc. driver         [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m application form.                                                            [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m **Vulnerability Discovery:**                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - The application is a Flask application using Python 3.10.20 with Werkzeug  [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m 3.1.7 and Jinja2 templating engine                                           [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - The `/application` endpoint displays a driver application form with        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m fields: name, email, phone, experience, license                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Form data is submitted to `/submit` via POST request                       [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - The `name` field is reflected in the thank you message without proper      [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m sanitization                                                                 [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m                                                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m **Vulnerability Confirmation:**                                              [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m - Initial test with `{{7*7}}` confirmed SSTI - the output showed `49`        [2;36m│[0m
[2;36m│[0m instead of the literal string                                                [2;36m│[0m
