[38;5;129m│[0m                                                                              [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m The fix would be to either:                                                  [38;5;129m│[0m
[38;5;129m│[0m - Use `render_template()` with proper variable passing instead of            [38;5;129m│[0m
